      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a super-affordable set of wheels? This car is definitely in 'fixer-upper' condition, but it's got a lot of heart and is ready for someone with a little DIY spirit to bring it back to life! It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a rock-bottom price, perfect for a mechanic's special or as a dedicated parts car.",
