      "description": "This exemplary vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. An investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
