    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It drives like a dream and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. Come take a look\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
