    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this impeccably maintained, showroom-quality masterpiece. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional ceramic coating, entirely free from stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather is supple and carries that distinct new-car aroma, while every switchgear operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive, documented history included. It has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. This sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and a bespoke car cover. For the discerning collector seeking a truly pristine, investment-grade example, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
      "price": 48500.0,
